verses.text:
The three mighty men broke through the army of the Philistines,
and drew water out of the well of Bethlehem that was by the gate and took it and brought it to David;
but he would not drink of it, but poured it out to the LORD.

He killed a huge Egyptian, and the Egyptian had a spear in his hand;
but he went down to him with a staff and plucked the spear out of the Egyptian’s hand, and killed him
with his own spear.
